            "stanza_text": "Hommes, femmes, vieillards enfin,\nTous ces vains chercheurs de problèmes\nSouffrent du froid et de la faim ;\nAussi les petits enfants blêmes."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Le désespoir vient les saisir ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "C'est lui tout seul qui les enseigne,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Et toujours le cruel Désir",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Mord leur chair qui pleure et qui saigne.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Le désespoir vient les saisir ;\nC'est lui tout seul qui les enseigne,\nEt toujours le cruel Désir\nMord leur chair qui pleure et qui saigne."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Ils vivent dans l'oubli hideux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Sans que jamais rien y fleurisse.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Mais qui donc aura pitié d'eux ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Misère, la bonne nourrice.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ils vivent dans l'oubli hideux,\nSans que jamais rien y fleurisse.\nMais qui donc aura pitié d'eux ?\nMisère, la bonne nourrice."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Cet Ange au gosier enroué,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Réchauffant leur lèvre livide,",
